message.entry: Error in matlab.mapreduce.DeploySparkMapReducer. CTF File ''{0}'' does not exist.
Map-Reduce paradigm is unsupported for matlab.mapreduce.DeploySparkMapReducer. Use matlab.mapreduce.DeployHadoopMapReducer instead.
Class matlab.mapreduce.DeploySparkMapReducer can only be used in deployed mode on a Linux platform.
Class matlab.mapreduce.DeploySparkMapReducer can only be used for Spark clusters.
SparkLogLevel property is not supported for this version of Spark. Consider using Spark version 1.4 or higher.
